'From Squeak3.4 of 1 March 2003 [latest update: #5170] on 29 March 2003 at 6:47:54 pm'!"Change Set:		RemoveScamperDate:			29 March 2003Author:			Adam SpitzRemoves Scamper from the image (assuming all references to it have already been removed)."String removeSelector: #replaceHtmlCharRefs.Smalltalk organization removeCategoriesMatching: 'Network-HTML*'.Smalltalk organization removeCategoriesMatching: 'Network-Web Browser'.Utilities informUser: 'Removing Scamper thumbnails from Tools flap and PartsBin. Please wait...' during: [	PartsBin clearThumbnailCache.	PartsBin cacheAllThumbnails.	Flaps replaceToolsFlap.].!